# Placeholder so `//go:embed all:frontend/dist` (gui/main.go) always finds a
# matching file. The real build output (index.html, assets/) is produced by
# `vite build` and is gitignored. Without this file, `go vet`/`go test` in CI
# fail with "pattern all:frontend/dist: no matching files found" because the
# quality-gate job does not build the frontend.
